Minima is a admin template for Joomla 1.6 that focus on minimalism to provide a better User Experience.

The template features Mootools 1.3 and lots of HTML5 & CSS 3 goodness.

( Full Joomla 1.6 installation included for testing. Minima's content is at 'administrator/templates/minima/' )

Intructions: 
==========
- Rename _installation to installation
- Run the installation proccess
- Install the sample data in the last step
- Rename installation back to _installation
